{"tid":1178073,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"《AION 永恆紀元》- 新職業「彩繪星」即將登場","createTime":"2019-05-30T07:17:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T07:57:36.000Z","uid":31029,"like":4,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"6b352e3b25d70bf99caaad2edbb3e1844333e760","tid":1178073,"uid":31029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T07:17:58.000Z","msg":"《AION 永恆紀元》7.0 新改版即將於 6 月 12 日推出，新戰鬥風格的職業「彩繪星」將同步現身。吉恩立今（29）日搶先釋出「彩繪星」相關介紹，帶領玩家感受新職業特色。<br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/M/2KU/13/73063dcc46afe6d9563e2bcdd214zxp5.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FM%2F2KU%2F13%2F73063dcc46afe6d9563e2bcdd214zxp5.JPG&h=496d81da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong>[size=4]<span style=\"color: gold;\">彩繪星：潮流魅力</span>[/size=5]</strong><br />\n時隔 5 年的藝術家職業「彩繪星」，在設定上融入了歐美的當代的街頭文化，有別於角色扮演遊戲固有的職業設定，如果說吟遊星是透過音律來展現自身藝術的話，那麼彩繪星則是藉由色彩塗鴉來渲染全世界，形成了遊戲中獨出一格的戰鬥風格。<br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/M/2KU/14/991d0ed46a91d0eef6d5d70ca614zxq5.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FM%2F2KU%2F14%2F991d0ed46a91d0eef6d5d70ca614zxq5.JPG&h=13285d62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong>[size=4]<span style=\"color: gold;\">彩繪星：誕生之路</span>[/size=5]</strong><br />\n在希埃爾主神的支援下，第一代彩繪星「依勒琳」研發的奧德顏料，並將有才能的弟子納入門下，進而開啟了彩繪星之路。但在大崩壞時期，希埃爾主神犧牲了，許多的彩繪星逐漸銷聲匿跡，剩下的彩繪星也輾轉四處，勉強保住了性命。<br />\n隨著歲月的流逝，襲擊亞特雷亞的暴風之日來臨時，記得希埃爾做出犧牲的彩繪星們，紛紛犧牲自己去挽救許多無辜的生命。當時的彩繪星的貢獻受到了肯定，因此晉升為正式的職業。<br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/M/2KU/15/bc2977c5dd73d38a77b76f870e14zxr5.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FM%2F2KU%2F15%2Fbc2977c5dd73d38a77b76f870e14zxr5.JPG&h=253e69fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/M/2KU/16/f99aa41aac5514d245c4b308ef14zxs5.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FM%2F2KU%2F16%2Ff99aa41aac5514d245c4b308ef14zxs5.JPG&h=40b6c2dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong>[size=4]<span style=\"color: gold;\">彩繪星：逆轉終結者</span>[/size=5]</strong><br />\n「彩繪星」具有物理性能，穿戴「彩繪器」與「物理系列長袍」透過噴射顏料給予敵人強烈打擊，除了高輸出的攻擊力之外，部份技能還具有束縛、氣絕、減速、擊退、出血、沉默、石化、吸血、引力等特殊效果，因此若隊伍中有彩繪星存在，將可能在劣勢情況下逆轉局勢，為團隊帶來勝利。<br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/M/2KU/17/60f4544e89295a148aa3c9aad614zxt5.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FM%2F2KU%2F17%2F60f4544e89295a148aa3c9aad614zxt5.JPG&h=2d933181&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bmCYRFdEXQ8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DbmCYRFdEXQ8&d=UJpThwxvwmp1Vrh6wv1Q1WXOOIBxzLj9jwnYVq%2FT7KE%3D&h=30bdaa89\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bmCYRFdEXQ8</a><br />\n官方為了迎接 7.0 改版到來，同步加開新伺服器「命運之神」，並於即日起至 6 月 12 日開放搶先創角，更多資訊將可至官網查詢。另外，官方指出，實況主「月希」、「Uzra」也將在 6 月 12 日加入 AION 戰場，分別代表天族、魔族創立軍團進行對抗。<br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/M/2KU/18/b37bf7faa74ec4fad6288daccc14zxu5.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FM%2F2KU%2F18%2Fb37bf7faa74ec4fad6288daccc14zxu5.JPG&h=2264c65a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e00222b83d77209830ba2cd08996949dd8737e45","tid":1178073,"uid":61724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T00:38:03.000Z","msg":"好似有新SER?"},{"pid":"e5189ab77525e41366864ddab1e88fff257460da","tid":1178073,"uid":55941,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T01:08:40.000Z","msg":"痴線仲未執?"},{"pid":"2c2873a173fbe9a659d1b79d9fdd0495c1cb9d71","tid":1178073,"uid":81077,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T01:21:30.000Z","msg":"仲未執<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d28771a8d071326a03925ff1910b582b169cafbc","tid":1178073,"uid":165499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T03:58:37.000Z","msg":"垃圾game<br />\n5.0以後無aion"},{"pid":"d3d940611bcd9d628f8fb2c3c8eb10484b7f3788","tid":1178073,"uid":51447,"like":0,"dislike":